Languages & Runtimes|Python|рҹ—‘ Remove Python|remove_python
Languages & Runtimes|Node.js|рҹ’ҡ Install NVM + Node LTS|install_nvm_node
Languages & Runtimes|Node.js|рҹ—‘ Remove NVM + Node|remove_nvm_node
Languages & Runtimes|Bun|рҹҘҹ Install Bun|install_bun
Languages & Runtimes|Bun|рҹ—‘ Remove Bun|remove_bun
Languages & Runtimes|PHP|рҹҗҳ Install PHP + Laravel|install_php_laravel
Languages & Runtimes|PHP|рҹ—‘ Remove PHP + Laravel|remove_php_laravel

