# в”Җв”Җ рҹҗҡ Shell в”Җв”Җ
Shell|Prompts|рҹ’ң Fancy Prompt (Purple-Pink)|create_fancy_prompt
Shell|Prompts|рҹ—‘ Remove Fancy Prompt (Purple-Pink)|remove_fancy_prompt
